title: Chemical Operator Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 2 weeks. I interviewed at Human Technologies (Seneca, SC) in Jun 2016
Interview Descriptions: DDI Testing, Drug Test, and a Plant Tour. Plant tour takes you thru the Dept. you will most likely be working at. DDI Test makes sure that you are capable of working at a "Chemical" Plant and have basic knowledge of machinery and Mathematics.
